SUMMARY:GriefShare
DESCRIPTION:GriefShare is a friendly\, caring group of people who will walk alongside you through one of life’s most difficult experiences. You don’t have to go through the grieving process alone.\nGriefShare meets for 13 weeks in the fall and spring on Wednesday evenings from 6:30-8:00pm.\nRegister\nhttps://www.griefshare.org/groups/264514
URL:https://www.calvarychurch.org/calendar/griefshare-33/
CATEGORIES:Pastoral Care,Website Calendar
END:VEVENT
