SUMMARY:Divorce Care
DESCRIPTION:Divorce Care is designed to provide support and biblical guidance for those who are facing impending divorce or have already gone through a divorce.\nDivorce Care meets for 13 weeks in the fall and spring on Wednesday evenings from 6:30-8:00pm.
